### Get API root
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

### Get single contact
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/64f5a5b5c7d9e8f0a1234567

### Create new contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Purple",
  "birthday": "1995-03-15"
}

### Update contact
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/64f5a5b5c7d9e8f0a1234567
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Robert",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "robert.johnson@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Red",
  "birthday": "1993-07-22"
}

### Delete contact
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/64f5a5b5c7d9e8f0a1234567

### Get Swagger documentation
GET http://localhost:8080/api-docs

### Get Swagger JSON
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-output.json